-- CNPC President Jiang Jiemin Says Cleaning Up Dalian Oil Spill Is `Crucial'
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-20T02:02:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/cnpc-president-jiang-jiemin-says-cleaning-up-dalian-oil-spill-is-crucial-.html

          
          
             Jiang Jiemin, the president of
China National Petroleum Corp. said cleaning up the oil spill
from its facilities in the northern port city of Dalian is
“crucial”, according to a company statement posted on its
website today.  
 Jiang visited the oil spill site on Sunday, the statement
said.  
          
          


  


        